name: TREEeyore
description: Internet art is one of my favorite forms of expressing art. It reminds me so much of creative writing and the freedom that comes with it. This genre of Art has always been my escapism from society and truly push myself to creative whatever I want in the most nonsensical way to most but to me it makes complete sense to me, and I can pour my heart and soul into it with deep meaning possible. Love at first computer.
